.TH "kvm_mips_write_compare" 9 "kvm_mips_write_compare" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
kvm_mips_write_compare \- Modify compare and update timer.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" kvm_mips_write_compare
.BI "(struct kvm_vcpu *vcpu "  ","
.BI "u32 compare "  ","
.BI "bool ack "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "vcpu" 12
Virtual CPU.
.IP "compare" 12
New CP0_Compare value.
.IP "ack" 12
Whether to acknowledge timer interrupt.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Update CP0_Compare to a new value and update the timeout.
If \fIack\fP, atomically acknowledge any pending timer interrupt, otherwise ensure
any pending timer interrupt is preserved.
